    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-09-08T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-09-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="769"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d769">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-09-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 8, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Confidential. Leader revolutionists mentioned Castro. After defeat gathered about
                    3,000 men. Government troops have not attacked. <pb facs="0890" n="794"
                        xml:id="pg_794"/> Trying mass forces. Revolution aided prominent political
                    refugees Curaçao. Government may succeed. Has 7,000 troops. Situation same
                    second cable 6th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
